  "text": "Two genes encoding for the formate dehydrogenase subunits were sequenced previously [CITATION_1] . For sequencing the whole cluster, T. litoralis partial genomic DNA library from EcoRI-XbaI digested genomic DNA was prepared in pBluescript SK+ vector. The labeled insert of pLHU1/1 clone was used to fish out the clone pFhl6 ( Fig. 1A.) , which was further subcloned and sequenced. As a next step, the labeled fragment of the pFhl10 was used to iso-late the pFhl17 clone from BamHI-EcoRV T. litoralis partial genomic DNA library. These fragments were subcloned and their nucleotide sequences were determined on both strands by an Applied Biosystems 373 Stretch DNA sequencer.",
